Brandon was a US Coast Guard
veteran in the Public Affairs

00:05:57.090 --> 00:05:58.869
office.

00:05:58.869 --> 00:06:01.160
He was on duty a few blocks
from the World Trade Center

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:03.950
and witnessed the attacks
and the Maritime evacuation

00:06:03.950 --> 00:06:05.320
