ODA 595 is also known
as the Horse Soldiers,

00:08:36.289 --> 00:08:39.320
for those of you who've
heard about that group

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:41.230
of extraordinary men.

00:08:41.230 --> 00:08:43.049
Mark retired from the
Army and continues

00:08:43.049 --> 00:08:45.540
to do contract work
in Afghanistan,

00:08:45.540 --> 00:08:49.380
and he is working on a
book about his experiences.

00:08:49.380 --> 00:08:51.510
He wants to write it himself
from his perspective,

00:08:51.510 --> 00:08:52.640
along with his teammates.

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:54.223
And that's something
that we're really

00:08:54.223 --> 00:08:57.090
excited to read
when it comes out.

00:08:57.090 --> 00:09:00.482
Scotty Neal, US Army
Special Forces veteran,

00:09:00.482 --> 00:09:02.690
Director of Strategic
Development for the Green Beret

00:09:02.690 --> 00:09:05.230
Foundation from Tampa, Florida.

00:09:05.230 --> 00:09:07.100
Scott was in a Green
Beret training exercise

00:09:07.100 --> 00:09:08.190
