00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:16.760
He spent 25 years in
the Army Special Forces

00:09:16.760 --> 00:09:19.970
with multiple combat tours
in 5th Special Forces Group,

00:09:19.970 --> 00:09:22.120
and he was later a
Senior Enlisted Advisor

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:24.580
to the Director of the US
Special Operations Command's

00:09:24.580 --> 00:09:29.970
Interagency Task Force at
MacDell Air Force Base.

00:09:29.970 --> 00:09:30.570
Thank you.

